Author: JuBelen
Text: Thank you. I feel better today.

Author: pabstpumpkinbeer
Text: I'm sorry you're feeling that way. 1500 is still very restrictive; and at any rate, there is absolutely no way you can "ruin" your body in two days. You deserve love no matter how much you eat and no matter how much you weight and no matter what your body looks like. You deserve love. FULL STOP.
